            <a target="_blank" href="https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-js2/Syncfusion.EJ2.Charts.AccumulationSeries.html#Syncfusion_EJ2_Charts_AccumulationSeries_NeckHeight">NeckHeight</a> properties.
